{"tid":490752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【共享尿袋】一插即中「木馬程式」 黑客可遙控手機畀錢","createTime":"2017-12-06T02:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T05:42:05.000Z","uid":70985,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8f391776a34cc4b2a2fdbe34616f8b76c102c7","tid":490752,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171205/small/1512462125_fedb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171205%2Fsmall%2F1512462125_fedb.jpg&h=8c25d867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都市人十分依賴手機，假如手機沒電就會感到很無助，在內地幾乎每間餐廳或商場，都放滿「共享尿袋」（充電器），供有需要的人隨時使用，不過它們卻暗藏危機。內地媒體揭發，共享尿袋遭卻被黑客利用，插上即中毒，植入電腦病毒「木馬程式」來盜取手機的個人資料，甚至可以遙距控制手機，進行網上交易付款。<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體利用「共享尿袋」做實驗，發現在連接手機和充電寶的一刻，手機已被植入木馬程式，黑客可以利用電腦，遙距控制用家手機。用家除了照片簿、通話紀錄外洩，各個手機應用程式都可以被隨意打開，甚至可以進入「支付寶」等付款軟件消費和轉帳，還可以接收驗證短訊更改密碼。不但如此，即使拔掉「尿袋」，黑客依然可以控制手機。<br />\n專家指，目前市面上絕大多數的充電寶都是安全的，但不排除其中充斥著黑客「尿袋」，因改造一個「尿袋」成本不高，只需300元（人民幣‧約355港元），而且外觀與正常「尿袋」完全無分別，實在難分真假。<br />\n專家建議，最好的解決方法是自己買一個「尿袋」隨身攜帶；不過，假如必要使用「共享尿袋」，可透過以下3招防身，兔個人資料外露：<br />\n一、向需要手機系統授權的「尿袋」Say NO！<br />\n二、幫手機安裝一個殺毒軟件<br />\n三、用私家雲端（Share drive/iCloud）保存公司文件<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171205/57544024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171205%2F57544024&d=Dj16aHTGWLAWY3FyFSabljQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=3f79afcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171205%2F57544024&h=aa790e72\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171205/57544024</a>"},{"pid":"34acec64b37dc1e361ced8a29190d5700a395cde","tid":490752,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國仲有乜係無毒"},{"pid":"ef6f69476a708fe58d8d9768444faf8e34e08e8a","tid":490752,"uid":31656,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國仲有乜係無毒</blockquote><br />\n毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8152bb754de953159bf324ede06544b5af3f2b","tid":490752,"uid":44916,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國仲有乜係無毒</blockquote><br />\n毒藥"},{"pid":"33b7e4dad17b403f3a3fcbff1b4980c15c7a21d5","tid":490752,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國仲有乜係無毒</blockquote><br />\n毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc0165e3600ba5e63ecc194a11a891b1abc2f5a","tid":490752,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:12:39.000Z","msg":"ios免疫？"},{"pid":"3170ee20f1887e94b2b3d93d2fb6c60a511e0897","tid":490752,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國仲有乜係無毒</blockquote><br />\n老鼠藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860c9696f391588d5ca724bb49db6764d131f906","tid":490752,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ios免疫？</blockquote><br />\nAndroid係易d，iPhone應該JB左先會一插出事掛"},{"pid":"c0b0f2536860fb209fae8fbb9863b8d311f91345","tid":490752,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ios免疫？</blockquote><br />\nAndroid係易d，iPhone應該JB左先會一插出事掛</blockquote><br />\n呢家仲有人jb?"},{"pid":"c6cea9e